profile:
Armour Grade is one of the leading gutter, soffit, and fascia installation company in the Thompson-Okanagan-Shuswap and BC Interior. We provide 5" continuous gutter replacement services, leaf guards, and vented aluminum soffit and cladding services.
Armour Grade crews operate in all major cities in the BC Interior including Kelowna, Kamloops, Penticton, Vernon, and Salmon Arm.
We provide 5" continuous gutter replacement services, leaf guards, and vented aluminum soffit and cladding services. We offer a wide variety of rain gutter solutions and continuous gutters and eavestroughs, vented soffit solutions, and fascia cladding and replacements.
Visit our website or contact our office to learn more about our services which also include roof cleaning, demossing, gutter cleaning, gutter repairs, etc.
We only hire the best and use the best material and products to insure exceptional service quality and workmanship standard
